== 分布 ==
狗鱼科具有[[全北界|全北界]]分布。狗鱼属的七个[[物种|物种]]可以在[[欧亚|欧亚]]和[[北美|北美]]发现，而黑鱼属的三个种则局限在[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]和[[东西伯利亚|东西伯利亚]]。新荫鱼属的分布最窄，唯一现存的种只在[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]]的[[奥林匹克半岛|奥林匹克半岛]]被发现。

在北美洲还发现了两个已灭绝的属''Estesesox''和''Oldmanesox''。''[[Estesesox|Estesesox]]''的化石主要存在于兰斯组、[[地狱溪组|地狱溪组]]、老人组、福莫斯特组和[[牛奶河_(亚伯达—蒙大拿)|牛奶河]]组等[[组_(地质学)|底层组]]内；''[[Oldmanesox|Oldmanesox]]''化石主要存在与老人组<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Wilson|first1=Mark V. H.|last2=Brinkman|first2=Donald B.|last3=Neuman|first3=Andrew G.|date=September 1992|title=Cretaceous Esocoidei (Teleostei): early radiation of the pikes in North American fresh waters|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/product/identifier/S0022336000020849/type/journal_article|journal=Journal of Paleontology|language=en|volume=66|issue=5|pages=839–846|doi=10.1017/S0022336000020849|issn=0022-3360}}</ref>。

== 行为 ==
虽然体型和口形大不相同，所有狗鱼科的现存物种都是依赖视觉的伏击型[[掠食者|掠食者]]，会吞咬任何能够塞进嘴里的猎物，其中狗鱼和黑鱼还都有[[同类相食|同类相食]]的行为<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Giles|first1=N.|last2=Wright|first2=R. M.|last3=Nord|first3=M. E.|date=1986|title=Cannibalism in pike fry, Esox lucius L.: some experiments with fry densities|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1095-8649.1986.tb04930.x|journal=Journal of Fish Biology|language=en|volume=29|issue=1|pages=107–113|doi=10.1111/j.1095-8649.1986.tb04930.x|issn=1095-8649|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527095413/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1095-8649.1986.tb04930.x|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=McPhail|first=J.D.|date=1981-01-01|title=The Freshwater Fishes of Alaska, by J.E. Morrow|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.14430/arctic2730|journal=Arctic|volume=34|issue=3|doi=10.14430/arctic2730|issn=1923-1245}}</ref>。[[新荫鱼|新荫鱼]]虽然也会在[[产卵|产卵]]期出于[[领域_(动物)|领地意识]]攻击同类，但是通常不会吃掉同类<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Hagen|first1=D. W.|last2=Moodie|first2=G. E. E.|last3=Moodie|first3=P. F.|date=2011-02-14|title=Territoriality and courtship in the Olympic mudminnow (Novumbra hubbsi)|url=https://cdnsciencepub.com/doi/abs/10.1139/z72-148|journal=Canadian Journal of Zoology|volume=50|issue=8|pages=1111–1115|language=en|doi=10.1139/z72-148|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527100335/https://cdnsciencepub.com/doi/abs/10.1139/z72-148|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

